  "about_item": [
    "Dog Crate Furniture for 2 Dogs - Our rovibek dog crates can be set up in a corner to maximize space, used as two separate crates, or combined into a long crate table, making it adaptable for various needs. The divider can also be removed to accommodate larger dogs.",
    "2 Concealed Trays - 2 dog crate is equipped with two washable trays discreetly located at the bottom, easily accessible by opening the hinge. This design not only enhances the aesthetic appeal with the wooden strips but also offers convenience for cleaning up pet hair and food.",
    "Secure & Sturdy - Dog kennel indoor features MDF board, ensuring a healthier environment for your pets and family. The durable iron frame can support over 400 pounds on top, and the reinforced iron door frame is both stylish and chew-resistant, significantly extending the crate's lifespan.",
    "Adjustable Space - Our double dog crate features a removable divider, allowing you to effortlessly transition between one spacious enclosure or two separate rooms. This setup ensures that your furry companions have their own specific space, reducing interruptions and fighting.",
    "Adjustable Feet - The big dog crate features 6 adjustable feet for height adjustment, ensuring stability and reducing floor friction in various scenarios. The dog kennel furniture comes with installation tools and an instruction manual for easy assembly."
  ],
