        "text": "I was pleasantly surprised by this double crate. It looks and feels super nice. My two 50 pound dogs are already just lounging it with the doors open. I was concerned that the doors wouldn’t stay open and flush with the cage when not latched, but they do, so the dogs can go in and out. My dogs won’t break out or even attempt to so I can’t attest to that aspect. A mom and her two toddlers put this together in like two hours. Everything was packaged neatly and instructions were easy to read. I don’t normally bother with reviews but I thought I should because I spent a lot of time going back-and-forth on which cage to buy and I’m glad I chose this one.",
